Run the cron job, for every two days at 10pm to send the emails:

1. Add the cron job

    $ crontab -e
    0 22 */2 * * DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=nightreads.settings.production /home/ubuntu/nightreads/venv/bin/python3 manage.py send_email >> /home/ubuntu/nightreads/logs/cron_stdout.log 2>&1

2. Confirm it is added:

    $ crontab -l